Welcome to JSA's "Christ in Hymns, a 5th Live Experience with JSA"! We're excited to share this beautiful performance of some of our favorite hymns, sung with passion and reverence to our Lord. We would like to thank those who suggested hymns for this episode. At JSA, our mission is to spread the message of love, hope, and faith in our Lord Jesus Christ through our music ministry. Hymns have a unique power to connect us with our spiritual roots and bring us closer to God. You'll hear beloved hymns such as "I will Sing of Jesus' Love," "Oh what a wonderful Day!" "Shall we Gather At the River" and many more. We hope this episode inspires and blesses you. As a ministry, we rely on your support to continue creating music that touches hearts and souls. Kindly share these Blessings!
